  ('dietitian-moex-11467', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-092-4665e2ba', 'sub-dietitian-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '營養諮詢的過程分成幾個步驟，包括： 計畫 評估 評價 實施，其步驟的先後順序為： → → →   → → →   → → →   → → →', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:59+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e959493419d7", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ec7f59b9c927", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "092170", "c": "111", "s": "5001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "公共衛生營養學", "year": "092", "exam_name": "092年第二次醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、獸醫人員、心理師、呼吸治療師考試", "original_question_number": 31, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-11468', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-092-4665e2ba', 'sub-dietitian-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '一個人在參加體重控制班活動後，感到健康是重要的，然後產生動機，願意去實行一些體重控制的行為，而導致健康 的改善。請問屬於衛生教育的那一種學習領域？ 認知（Cognitive）  情意（Affective）  技能（Psychomotor）  適應（Adaptive）', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:59+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e959493419d7", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ec7f59b9c927", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "092170", "c": "111", "s": "5001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "公共衛生營養學", "year": "092", "exam_name": "092年第二次醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、獸醫人員、心理師、呼吸治療師考試", "original_question_number": 32, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
